history.content:
TECH TALK ALERT! If you’re interested in Northrop Grumman, internships, jobs, and/or Artificial Intelligence this opportunity is perfect for you!

 

PlexTech, a software consulting club at Cal, is hosting a Tech Talk on Wednesday, April 28th from 5-6pm PT with Northrop Grumman’s AI Architect, Tyler Dillstrom (PhD). This Tech Talk is open to everyone interested in learning more about The Three Waves of AI and all things that Northrop Grumman offers to people like YOU!

 

RSVP for this Talk at https://tinyurl.com/yjfb9mwx to receive an invitation to this event. If you have any questions, reach out to Jackson Bursch at Daniel.Bursch@ngc.com .

 

We at PlexTech look forward to seeing you there! You don't want to miss this!
history.subject: Northrop Grumman Tech Talk hosted by PlexTech
